    <h1>One-Legged Dancer</h1>
    <p>
      When Vinod Thakur lost his leg in an accident at a young age, many believed his dreams of dancing were over. But Vinod had a different rhythm in mind. With sheer determination, he taught himself to perform complex hip-hop and breakdance moves—balancing, flipping, and inspiring.
    </p>
    <p>
      He rose to fame on reality shows like *India’s Got Talent*, stunning judges and audiences alike with his raw skill and unmatched energy. Vinod proved that talent has no limits, and that even one leg is enough to chase dreams, leap into the spotlight, and uplift others through unstoppable passion.
    </p>

